      <t>&lt;p&gt;As required by Routing Protocol Criteria (RFC 1264), this report defines the applicability of the RIPng protocol within the Internet.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
